{"title":"扶桑诗草——仿日本俳句","authors":["黎宏"],"dates":[{"year":1980,"month":12,"day":2}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"扶桑诗草"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——仿日本俳句"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"北京大学学生友好访日团  黎宏"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"虹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和东京大学同学欢聚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"即席草成"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金风玉露浓，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"燕园东大飞长虹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日喜相逢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草坪郁葱葱，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"欢声笑语荡湖中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"七彩映碧空。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"两岸秋波涌，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"彩虹相连心相通，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"友情永珍重。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"京都赴奈良车上作"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赠俳人协会村井隆先生"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋雨任点滴，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奈良朦胧烟色里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珠帘掩秀仪。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金风携细雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里旅尘尽一洗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"点点是情意。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨打叶更绿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大珠小珠铺满地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江山正娇丽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蝉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"访唐招提寺有感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清音绕庭院，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨后荷叶珠正圆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"滴滴溶水面。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸣唱碧叶间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草木凝神花合眼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声扣心弦。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋月映澄天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大师一生是诗篇，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长吟永不倦。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}